org.supercsv.io
Class CsvMapWriter

java.lang.Object
  org.supercsv.io.AbstractCsvWriter
      org.supercsv.io.CsvMapWriter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ICsvMapWriter, ICsvWriter
public class CsvMapWriter
extends AbstractCsvWriter
implements ICsvMapWriter

The writer class capable of writing maps of different types to a CSV file. Notice that the cell processors can also be utilized when writing. E.g. they can help ensure that only numbers are written in numeric columns, that numbers are unique or the output does not contain certain characters or exceed specified string lengths.

Author:
Kasper B. Graversen
